      "title": "Four including gangster \u2019Pas Podda\u2019 injured in shooting near Gampaha court",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Four persons including underworld figure Saman Rohitha Perera alias \u2018Pas Podda\u2019 have been injured in a shooting outside the Gampaha Magistrate\u2019s Court this afternoon, police said.",
        "They said the injured were admitted to the Gampaha Hospital.",
        "According to the police, unidentified men arrived in a car and opened fire at 'Pas Podda\u2019 and others who were returning attending a court hearing."
      ],
